WEBVTT

00:00:01.135 --> 00:00:04.952
For my husband,
it was love at first sight.

00:00:04.976 --> 00:00:06.246
(Laughter)

00:00:06.270 --> 00:00:07.865
Here's what happened.

00:00:07.889 --> 00:00:09.839
Years ago, Rudy,

00:00:09.863 --> 00:00:13.926
who I had strictly put
in the friend zone at the time,

00:00:13.950 --> 00:00:16.410
came over to my house and met my dad,

00:00:16.434 --> 00:00:19.552
a pharmaceutical scientist
who had just retired

00:00:19.576 --> 00:00:21.783
after bringing a drug to market.

00:00:22.339 --> 00:00:23.672
My dad said,

00:00:23.696 --> 00:00:25.747
"Ah, you probably
wouldn't have heard of it.

00:00:25.771 --> 00:00:27.302
It's for IPF,

00:00:27.326 --> 00:00:30.334
idiopathic pulmonary fibrosis."